abstract: |
  A production-tested llama.cpp configuration for running Qwen3.5-35B-A3B (MoE) 
  on NVIDIA 16GB GPUs, achieving 124 t/s generation speed with 152K context and 
  vision enabled. Includes the discovery of a hard performance cliff at exactly 
  155,904 tokens caused by CUDA_Host buffer alignment, not VRAM overflow.
